  <description value="FHIR Body Height Profile - Copied FHIR Vital Sign Profile to remove .component.value quantity type constrain. More information can be found in GForge ticket #13796 or in the FHIR zulip chat https://chat.fhir.org/#narrow/stream/implementers/subject/Vital.20signs.20supporting.20observations." />
